" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2735d1aa57c019b72e27d4bf7329e2c6c2b02b","tid":399872,"uid":21255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"豬蛇我CV寫自己工作經驗係統一六國<br />\n點解仲未有interview ?"},{"pid":"ef0d329ff87de63bd7d4619563f26685fdaf52cc","tid":399872,"uid":36497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T16:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豬蛇我CV寫自己工作經驗係統一六國<br />\n點解仲未有interview ?</blockquote><br />\n你in青山醫院？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d9b1dd296d4e8651f8532a34ea3971b905329a","tid":399872,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T16:32:46.000Z","msg":"屌你呀哥好過渣波"},{"pid":"71914473eec5b97953b447557455e9625052eb30","tid":399872,"uid":36497,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T16:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講d野都好基本...有無d深入d&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n咩cover letter 改改去先send 呢d講左幾十年&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n呢d野都錯 個人都廢，仲可以幫到佢d咩？</blockquote><br />\n簡單d講<br />\n<br />\nasso hd 仔+無經驗 del 得<br />\n8大仔 waiting list 可再睇<br />\n3大 會in左先<br />\n<br />\ncv 5,6頁咁多，我唔撚會睇<br />\n寫1-2 頁 最好<br />\n<br />\n<strong>個人資料</strong>(中英文名姓別電話email地址)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>career objective</strong> (如果唔知寫乜，唔好勉強去寫，唔好寫柒左)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>學歷</strong>(寫大學中學就ok)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>extra curricular activities</strong> (去過exchange，去非洲做義工，做peer mnetor果d正氣野，如果無可以不寫，諗下呢d活動同份工有咩連繫）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>工作經驗+簡單講下工作範疇</strong>（如你係fg，寫埋part time job ，起碼唔會令人覺得你是廢青)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>professional qualifications</strong> (如有才寫，童軍獎章果d咪撚寫)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>computer skill</strong> (識d乜就寫乜,Photoshop 呀 word excel 之類)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Language skill</strong> (中英普+外語)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>references</strong>( 如有)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>date of availability</strong> <br />\n<br />\n咁樣都有1.5頁了"},{"pid":"382bd42d0e5d6429d555e66357f5f1aeedf70f2c","tid":399872,"uid":36143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"re